section.def:
Authority
                (市建局) means the Urban Renewal Authority
            established under section 3;

subparagraph.content:
the amount of administrative or other costs and
                                                expenses incurred by the Appeal Board in relation to
                                                the hearing and determination of an appeal;

paragraph.content:
obstructs the Secretary, the Authority or any person authorized in writing
                    by the Secretary or the Authority under delegated authority from entering or
                    inspecting any land or any premises on it under this section;

to furnish after the expiry of the financial year a report on the
                        affairs of the Authority for that year, a copy of its accounts therefor, and
                        the auditor’s report on the accounts;
